                "text": "Vulnerability CVE-2024-34459\nSeverity: low\nPackage: libxml2\nVersion: 2.12.5-10.el10\nFix Version: \nType: rpm\nLocation: /usr/lib/sysimage/rpm/rpmdb.sqlite\nData Namespace: redhat:distro:redhat:10\nLink: [CVE-2024-34459](https://access.redhat.com/security/cve/CVE-2024-34459)",
